ue from a core\ngroup of users should be more aggressive and protective of its user base than a\nfirm that generates revenue uniformly from its users.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2015 02:45:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2015 22:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-02"}
