ally, our proposed optimal Cosserat rotations\n$rpolar^{\\pm}_{\\mu,\\mu_c}(F)$ act in the \"plane of maximal strain\" and our\npreviously obtained explicit formulae for planar optimal Cosserat rotations in\n$SO(2)$ reveal themselves as a simple special case. Further, we derive the\nassociated reduced energy levels of the Cosserat shear--stretch energy and\ncriteria for the existence of non-classical optimal rotations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2015 14:22:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-22"}
